Package ohos.data.orm

Class OrmObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • ohos.data.orm.OrmObject

  • public class OrmObject
extends Object
    Represents entities in the object-relational mapping (ORM) database.

    A row in a relational database (RDB) table corresponds to an entity in the ORM database. Before operating entities in the ORM database, you need to create an entity class that inherits from OrmObject and annotate it with @Entity.

    Since:
    1
    See Also:
